   ],
   "source": [
    "games.flip_a_coin()"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "Next up is rolling a die. Let's make sure it isn't biased by plotting a histogram of many rolls:"
